  "display_name": "Public Relations and Crisis Communication",
  "description": "This cluster of papers focuses on crisis communication, particularly the use of social media, in managing and responding to various crises such as natural disasters, organizational crises, and public health emergencies. It explores the role of public relations, stakeholder engagement, and dialogic communication in shaping effective crisis management strategies. The papers also delve into the impact of social media on organizational reputation, community engagement, and emergency response.",
